#: ../userguides/custom_pipelines.rst:4 df7ab7deec8e4406b048aa3b22528312
msgid "There are several options of model customization in Mapflow."
msgstr ""

#: ../userguides/custom_pipelines.rst:6 cbc5814bf0e54f08b89faf1e2eb86d0f
msgid ""
"You request access to a specific model based on your use case and data, "
"and we train it for you and connect it to Mapflow."
msgstr ""

#: ../userguides/custom_pipelines.rst:8 0e419f2ae0f34b339ff992c9abb85a25
msgid ""
"You choose one of the pre-trained models that are not included in the "
"standard Mapflow pipelines and test it with your data or on your area to "
"decide if it's applicable or requires additional training."
msgstr ""

#: ../userguides/custom_pipelines.rst:10 e382869bfeb94963bf928dbb42e87a26
msgid ""
"You train your own model with custom data and request our support to "
"connect it to your account to leverage your model with the Mapflow "
"workflow engine."
msgstr ""

